			        	</div>
				        
		        	</div>
				</div>
								<div>
					<div class="testi-item">
						<div class="ttext">
				        	“I’ve been using Gigenet for about 18 months, and I’ve never had a better experience with another datacenter. They provide extremely high levels of service.”				        </div>
						<div class="t-head">
				        	<div class="tinfo">
				        		<h6>Scott Kennedy</h6>
				        						        	</div>
			        	</div>
				        
		        	</div>
				</div>
								<div>
					<div class="testi-item">
						<div class="ttext">
				        	"We received a large DDoS attack causing it to go offline. Our hosting provider at the time was unable to stop the attacks for 2 days. GigeNET got our site up within hours of contacting them and WE STAYED UP!!! We now host ALL of our services exclusively with GigeNET!"				        </div>
						<div class="t-head">
				        	<div class="tinfo">
				        		<h6>freecodesource. com</h6>
				        						        	</div>
			        	</div>
				        
		        	</div>
